ds.util
Class Bag<T>

java.lang.Object
  ds.util.Bag<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class Bag<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Collection<T>, Iterable<T>

This class implements the Collection interface as a user-specified finite array; random access to an element is provided by the grab method.
